name: Deeter the Dino
description: Deeter gets a little nervous sometimes and finds that a hug from a friend makes him feel much better. When he’s not hugging he is drawing and painting pictures. He has an art studio where friends and neighbors can come and create together. He also plays a mean saxophone! Favorite things: green crayons, spinach, jazz, watching movies Each plush doll measures approximately 18” Materials: soft anti-pill fleece, cotton and felt Please allow 7-10 business days for delivery as each doll is made by hand. If you have a specific date you need your product delivered, please let me know and I can work with you to meet your deadline. Thank you so much! ©2011 Leeann Leftwich Zajas

name: Ray the Robot
description: Ray is a recycled, solar-powered robot who loves the sun. To get out his nervous energy, Ray runs the junk yard/recycling center in the clouds to help out other robots when one of their parts needs fixing. He spends a lot of time at the library and practices yoga in the morning since he tends to get a little “amped.” Favorite things: video games, the sun, collecting bottlecaps, super heroes Each doll measures approximately 18” Materials: soft anti-pill fleece, cotton and felt Please allow 7-10 business days for delivery as each doll is made by hand. If you have a specific date you need your product delivered, please let me know and I can work with you to meet your deadline. Thank you so much! ©2011 Leeann Leftwich Zajas

name: Miss Kitty the Kitten
description: Miss Kitty is a shy, orange kitten who loves to dance and sing! She runs a dance studio where she regularly puts on recitals for all of her friends in the clouds. Miss Kitty knows  how important it is to practice, so she does so every day. Favorite things: cotton candy, bubble gum, magic tricks, puppies Each doll measures approximately 18” Materials: soft anti-pill fleece, cotton, felt, and tulle.
